data.description: You don't want to miss this beautiful 2 story home located in sought after Lamar County! This beauty was just built in 2022 with the above ground pool installed last year! Interior features a large master bedroom with his and hers closets, 3 large secondary bedrooms, open floor plan, lots of natural light and a great floorpan for a large family! Home sits on over an acre lot on a quiet street with a large deck surrounding the new above ground pool. This one won't last long! Call today for a showing!
